{"tid":1269921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話想燒國旗區旗嘅唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:33:56.000Z","uid":237962,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4aafda1864f7eb44abb2d37b690c210d910ea1","tid":1269921,"uid":237962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:57:06.000Z","msg":"見到有人開post唔知燒國旗區旗係香港犯法所以想爹兩句<br />\n係香港燒國旗區旗屬於犯法，仲有好多案例。<br />\n最早係1999年 「<span style=\"color: blue;\">HKSAR訴吳恭劭(HKSAR v Ng Kung Siu (1999) 2 HKCFAR 442)</span> 」 一案中，兩名被告被控兩項侮辱國旗及區旗法（《國旗條例》第7條&amp;《區旗條例》第7條）。雖然上訴庭判無罪，但<span style=\"color: red;\">政府死纏爛打上訴至終院</span>。最終5名大法官<span style=\"color: red;\">一致裁定被告有罪</span>，需要簽$4000守行為1年。當時終院首席法官李國能係判詞指香港雖然保障言論自由，但該裁決並非針對被告所帶出嘅訊息，單純只針對損壞國旗區旗呢個行為。<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">裁決並無妨礙人權及言論自由</span><br />\n呢個只係其中之一，仲有好多類似案例：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170410/mobile/bkn-20170410180445726-0410_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170410%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170410180445726-0410_00822_001.html&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXFpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=ea1fca25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170410/mobile/bkn-20170410180445726-0410_00822_001.html</a><br />\n破壞損毀國旗國徽最高刑罰<span style=\"color: red;\">判監3年罰款5萬</span><br />\n破壞損毀國旗國徽一樣（但如果巡簡易程序定罪就判監1年罰款1萬）<br />\n雖然過往判刑唔係話好重，但依家港共政權決心用法律黎做打壓工具<br />\n無所不用其極，我覺得今次法院有機會聲稱要有阻嚇作用而判1年幾甚至2年以上，至少要有心理準備要打到上終院<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕</span>嘅話好有機會被入罪<br />\n<br />\n我打呢段嘢目的純粹希望各位清楚了解呢樣嘢所背負嘅風險，值與唔值請自行判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"901b91cfadb8105f5e46fe766c52b097256d23b0","tid":1269921,"uid":237962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"549407b377fd3a88be750c680bc70921f1d1a2df","tid":1269921,"uid":61398,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbfaeb24b7e68db699f821c82e69be6c3ccd4c58","tid":1269921,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:49.000Z","msg":"唔被捕呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65878daec4849c6ba8ca466ded60b39e2867981","tid":1269921,"uid":237962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbfaeb24b7e68db699f821c82e69be6c3ccd4c58","tid":1269921,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:49.000Z","msg":"唔被捕呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed7b237235272f50aaa679c7de4984452b0a6bb","tid":1269921,"uid":230806,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108f71229fc17781c30aff03c3a1f54f2690eb2f","tid":1269921,"uid":237962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"549407b377fd3a88be750c680bc70921f1d1a2df","tid":1269921,"uid":61398,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"梗係驚啦<br />\n克驚喎<br />\n所以如果唔係short左我都盡量避免被克驚拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06985468563689f359c004b16e6e158a3f4b5c39","tid":1269921,"uid":253409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ed7b237235272f50aaa679c7de4984452b0a6bb","tid":1269921,"uid":230806,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港要反共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dbe9e1c71ef3b784091a6